    "description": "Red Crucible Tanks is a free-to-play game where you can engage in intense online armored vehicle battles against players from around the world. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279580/extras/d172a33f6049ee3cc873ebf217ee123b.avif?t=1724174860\" width=600 height=244 /></span><br><br>Wage war with the world’s deadliest armored combat vehicles. Engage in furious player versus player armored vehicle combat to dominate various theaters of war ranging from: the fields of Europe, jungle islands, and soon European cities and scorched desert wastelands!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279580/extras/ebda7413daf609ff321b515ffea69057.poster.avif?t=1724174860\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279580/extras/ebda7413daf609ff321b515ffea69057.webm?t=1724174860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279580/extras/ebda7413daf609ff321b515ffea69057.mp4?t=1724174860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have at your disposal iconic fighting machines ranging from Cold War to modern combat vehicles and tanks. Feel the exhilaration and power as you dominate, crush and smash your opponents on the battlefields of war!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279580/extras/b5483e5dd55b60a5c31b613e867ef89a.avif?t=1724174860\" width=600 height=244 /></span><br><br>Master your knowledge of the various vehicles of war. Learn their strengths and weaknesses in order to fight your way to the top and claim victory!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279580/extras/fdae406216eb59dd1c75079f09d8bb40.avif?t=1724174860\" width=600 height=244 /></span>",
